         <div xml:id="main">
            <head type="incipit">
               <supplied reason="XTF-compatibility">Chief Secretary's Office ¶ Melbourne 24th April 1883 ¶ Sir, ¶  ¶ I have the honor to acknowledge the receipt of your letter of the 16th instant, ¶ M to T. Wilson, 16 April 1883(in this edition as 83-0...</supplied>
            </head>
            <p rend="number" xml:lang="en">83.04.24</p>
            <p rend="correspondent" xml:lang="en">From Thomas Wilson</p>
            <p rend="location" xml:lang="en">No. 1551, p. 1055, unit 63, VPRS 1187/P, outward registered correspondence, VA 475 Chief Secretary's Department, Public Record Office of Victoria</p>
            <space dim="vertical" unit="lines" quantity="1"/>
            <p rend="letter"
               style="font-size: 12pt; hyphenate: false; text-align: end; "
               xml:lang="en">Chief Secretary's Office</p>
            <p rend="letter"
               style="font-size: 12pt; hyphenate: false; text-align: end; "
               xml:lang="en">Melbourne 24th April 1883</p>
            <p rend="letter"
               style="font-size: 12pt; hyphenate: false; "
               xml:lang="en">Sir,</p>
            <p rend="letter"
               style="font-size: 12pt; hyphenate: false; "
               xml:lang="en">
               <space dim="horizontal" extent="tab"/>I have the honor to acknowledge the receipt of your letter of the 16th instant,<seg rend="FootnoteReference" style="font-size: 8pt; ">
                  <note type="footnote" xml:id="_ftn0" n="1">
                     <p rend="FootnoteText"
                        style="margin-left: 0.3333in; text-indent: -0.3333in; font-size: 9pt; hyphenate: false; "
                        xml:lang="en">
                        <space unit="chars" quantity="1"/>
                        <space dim="horizontal" extent="tab"/>M to T. Wilson, 16 April 1883<space unit="chars" quantity="1"/>(in this edition as 83-04-16b).</p>
                  </note>
               </seg>
               <space unit="chars" quantity="1"/>and with reference thereto beg to inform you that the amount required for the purchase of the collection of dried plants of the late Dr Sonder of Hamburg viz. £900 (less premium) will by the outgoing mail, be transmitted to the Agent General, who has been desired to place himself in communication with Mrs Sonder, and to arrange for the early transmission to this colony of the collection referred to.</p>
            <p rend="valediction"
               style="font-size: 12pt; margin-left: 1.75in; hyphenate: false; "
               xml:lang="en">I have the honor to be,</p>
            <p rend="valediction"
               style="font-size: 12pt; margin-left: 1.75in; hyphenate: false; "
               xml:lang="en">
               <space dim="horizontal" extent="tab"/>Sir,</p>
            <p rend="valediction"
               style="font-size: 12pt; margin-left: 1.75in; hyphenate: false; "
               xml:lang="en">
               <space dim="horizontal" extent="tab"/>
               <space dim="horizontal" extent="tab"/>Your most obedient servant,</p>
            <p rend="valediction"
               style="font-size: 12pt; margin-left: 1.75in; hyphenate: false; "
               xml:lang="en">
               <space dim="horizontal" extent="tab"/>
               <space dim="horizontal" extent="tab"/>
               <space dim="horizontal" extent="tab"/>T. R. Wilson</p>
            <space dim="vertical" unit="lines" quantity="1"/>
            <p rend="letter"
               style="font-size: 12pt; hyphenate: false; "
               xml:lang="en">The Government Botanist</p>
         </div>
      </body>
